><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>3.<strong> <\/strong>Get dressed-as if you&#x2019;re not working from home!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As nice as it can be to lounge around in pyjamas all day, it minimizes productivity and can make you a bit sleepy. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>One key tip to work from home is to get dressed and ready, like a normal workday. This can immediately make you feel more ready to take on the day, and increase efficiency.<br><br><strong>Luckily:<\/strong> There is no dress code when working from home! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer.jpg\" alt=\"tips work freelancer\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"tips work freelancer\" class=\"wp-image-21287 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121749\/tips-work-freelancer-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content