 <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>8. <strong>Change your environment<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A designated area to work from home provides more structure. However, it&#x2019;s also beneficial to change the environment sometimes, in order to get a fresh perspective. This could be to a new area in the home (with a new outlook), or by setting yourself up in a cafe. Most cafes have WiFi and electric sockets now, in order to cater to freelancers and those working from home. Additionally, seeing other people working in the cafe can help motivate you to stay on track with your tasks.<br><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer.jpg\" alt=\"best cafes work freelancer\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best cafes work freelancer\" class=\"wp-image-21296 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-work-freelancer-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121726\/best-cafes-w