speed internet connection, printers, and sometimes added extras, like a gym, swimming pool, classes, or free tea and coffee. The main benefit though is being able to socialize with other people, who work within different sectors. Making friends and being a part of a co-working community can be very inspiring and greatly increase your efficiency.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read about some of our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/bali\/cafes-work-canggu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"favorite cafes to work in Canggu, Bali (opens in a new tab)\">favorite cafes to work in Canggu, Bali<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121704\/co-working-space.jpg\" alt=\"co working space\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"co working space\" class=\"wp-image-21329 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121704\/co-working-space.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121704\/co-working-space-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121704\/co-working-space-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121704\/co-working-space-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content