motions via text. This makes a video call the best option for faster and more effective communication. It&#x2019;s also a great way of generating ideas with each other. Two brains are better than one!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Must-read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-make-money-online\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to make money online, 13 jobs and where to find them<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>11. Eat tasty but healthy meals while working from home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good food is a good mood! Eating healthily, and getting creative in the kitchen, forces you to take a good &#x2018;break&#x2019; from work. Skip those easy-to-grab sugary snacks, as they will cause tiredness and decrease productivity.  Instead, eat healthy foods to keep the brain in focus. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Just because food is &#x2018;healthy&#x2019;, doesn&#x2019;t mean it can&#x2019;t be tasty. Mix together a delicious bowl of fruits, nuts, and seeds, or make a natural peanut butter banana sandwich.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Top tip:<\/strong> Don&#x2019;t skip breakfast! Studies show eating breakfast improves concentration throughout the day.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home.jpg\" alt=\"tips work from home\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"tips work from home\" class=\"wp-image-21288 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121745\/tips-work-from-home-768x512.jpg 