 present while working from home or in a cafe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home.jpg\" alt=\"best tips work from home\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best tips work from home\" class=\"wp-image-21293 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121731\/best-tips-work-from-home-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2